<% provide(:title, "Become an ambassador") %>
<% provide(:description, "Want to get extra work as an ambassador? Create a profile, get approved, accept booking requests and get paid!") %>
<div class="hiw container-fluid">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="how-to-get-work-background">
			<div class="layer">
			  <div class="hiw-layer">
			    <div class="how-header">
			      <div class="title">
			        <h1>Become an Ambassador</h1>
			      </div> <!-- title -->
			      <div class="subheader">
			        <h3>Learn how to book events in your area.</h3>
			      </div> <!-- subheader -->
			    </div> <!-- how-header -->
			  </div> <!-- hiw-layer -->
			</div>
		</div> <!-- how-background -->
	</div> <!-- row -->
	<div class="content">
		<div class="col-md-4 sidebar">
			<%= render 'layouts/public/hiw' %>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-8">
			<div class="row" id="signup">
				<div class="panel">
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="col-md-8">
							<h3>List Your Profile</h3>
							<p>Signing up is free. First, tell us about yourself and your event experience. Than we will assist you to create your profile.</p>
							<p>When you're ready to start working events, you can publish your profile for the world to see.</p>
							<!-- <small class="learn-more"><a href>Learn More</a></small> -->
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4 text-center hiw-icon">
							<i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o fa-5x"></i>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>				

			<div class="row" id="approved">
				<div class="panel">
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="col-md-8">
							<h3>Respond to Requests</h3>
							<p>Companies who love your profile will want to book you for their event! On Shyft, you have the option to require companies to send a booking request or allow certain companies to book you instantly through Instant Book.</p>
							<p>Once you have received a booking request you will have 24 hours to respond or it will be cancelled.</p>
							<!-- <small class="learn-more"><a href>Learn More</a></small> -->
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4 text-center hiw-icon">
							<i class="fa fa-refresh fa-5x"></i>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row" id="accept">
				<div class="panel">
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="col-md-8">
							<h3>Work Events</h3>
							<p>Once you have a confirmed event, itâ€™s time to prepare for the event! The company will contact you to set up training so you can put the brand's best foot forward when you represent them.</p>
							<p>Getting paid is simple. On top of being a great ambassador, you just have to check-in and check-out on time from the event and you will receive an email or PayPal transfer within 48 hours after it ends.</p>
							<!-- <small class="learn-more"><a href>Learn More</a></small> -->
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4 text-center hiw-icon">
							<i class="fa fa-check-square-o fa-5x"></i>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<%= render 'layouts/public/questions' %>